{"tid":1761401,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"《人民日報》：美國絕非香港恩主　為何感恩美干預","createTime":"2019-11-29T01:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T02:31:41.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7e8b2f575bcb485aa6434da680b4a00698b69cba","tid":1761401,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:49:32.000Z","msg":"《人民日報》發表文章，批評美方不顧中方多次嚴正交涉，悍然將所謂《香港人權與民主法案》簽署成法，是對中國內政的粗暴干涉，是對香港同胞共同利益的嚴重損害，是對全體中國人民的直接挑釁。<br />\n<br />\n文章以「美國絕不是香港的恩主」為題，指出一些香港人將赤裸裸的霸權行徑當作最好的感恩節禮物，奴相十足，醜態百出。美國反華勢力與香港反對派狼狽為奸，成為極端暴力事件的主要推手，是人盡皆知的事實，反問為何反對派要借外人之手來制裁生之養之的香港、又對美國的干預感恩戴德。<br />\n<br />\n文章強調，「美國與你們同在」的宣示，不過是物色「棋子」的謊言。關於取消香港「單獨關稅區」地位等制裁內容，與人權、民主無關。香港經貿一旦受挫，將在投資信心、企業經營、市民就業等方面產生鏈式反應，影響香港的繁榮穩定。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495070-20191129.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495070-20191129.htm&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=2da38695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495070-20191129.htm&h=44ff43ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495070-20191129.htm</a>"},{"pid":"53c4a9359c771f6c8e9c20f3cebad65b183cc753","tid":1761401,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://sc1.passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201501/vy8nme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsc1.passiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201501%2Fvy8nme.jpg&h=0bbd9191&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"386b6310aec3e02caebbc763f7b25a82e797f80b","tid":1761401,"uid":759,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:54:05.000Z","msg":"係唔係恩主唔緊要,係你仇家就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"315c1ff38e695250003a19c8355dcbfcc4c1fd13","tid":1761401,"uid":52459,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy"